{
  "stem": "6719.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All right, to continue about the a so-called commanding officer of the staff kommando, the SK, the penal kommando.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "His name was Joseph Eckhardt, E-C-K--H-A-R-D-T.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was-- his rank was unterscharfuhrer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think that is a non-commissioned officer, something like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't- I don't know the equivalent ranks in English.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But that's what he was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he was a vicious, very vicious beast.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, as I said before, that the-- one was supposed to only have two days or three days to live down there, because this was-- that's what it was supposed to be, a penal colony [INAUDUIBLE].",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "People went in there to-- to get tortured and murdered.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that's it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That's the end of the story.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I've seen him do things like-- oh, there's one particular thing where apparently he, he came in to the barrack in front of everybody.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And while we were in roll call, roll call in that outside, outside the barrack, you know, between the wall and the barracks.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he said to the block [NON-ENGLISH], or the block elder-- his name was Emil Betnarek.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was- he had a red triangle.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He was of Polish origin, but I think that he also spoke a little German.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Political, a political prisoner.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And also the designation P-- the letter P was in there, that you knew.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "F was French, P was this, and so on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he told them that he received information that we will have to get another 10 prisoners in there, but there's no place.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he said get rid of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this is established, because there are eyewitnesses to this, including this boy here.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Betnarek went and got 10 people out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there was a little fella down there, was maybe 15 or 16 years old.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
